2026-06-28 22:27:10,838 826849 DEBUG mcpp_git running: git commit -m docs: MESSAGES_SPEC.md 2.0.0 — mesh-gw owns entire message state machine

Architectural rewrite. mesh-gw is the single authority for all send-state
transitions: outbound packet tracking, ROUTING_APP ACK correlation via
request_id, 30s asyncio timeout, and message_status event emission.
node-dash persists status to SQLite and relays message_status to browser.
Browser is a rendering terminal only — no timers, no packet-ID correlation,
no ackStatus state machine. Authority boundaries table corrected throughout.
from_num parseInt(MAC) bug documented. "Not yet implemented" section lists
all required code changes.

