2026-06-28 22:53:37,053 826849 DEBUG mcpp_git.tool CALL dev_commit args={'message': 'feat: move 5 browser business decisions to node-dash\n\nws-relay.js:\n- _ownNums(): derives gateway node numbers from live _liveNodeIds map\n- _enrichMessages(): pre-computes direction, thread_root_packet_id, is_orphan,\n  reply_depth for every message_history row — browser receives these ready to render\n- message_history send now calls _enrichMessages() before pushing to client\n- _seenLivePktIds: session-scoped Set cleared on bridge reconnect; suppresses\n  duplicate TEXT_MESSAGE_APP packet events before broadcast (live dedup)\n\napp-messages.js:\n- _applyMessageRows: reads r.direction from server; reads thread fields from server;\n  removes ownNums Set computation; removes _seenPacketIds.add()\n- displayMessages(): replaces recursive getRoot()/childrenOf tree walk with flat\n  sort on pre-computed threadRootPktId/replyDepth — no business logic in browser\n- sendMessage(): removes 3-attempt retry loop (single POST, failure is final)\n- sendMessage(): removes `|| this.activeNodeId` sender fallback — if no msgFrom,\n  shows error toast and returns; txEntry sets threadRootPktId/replyDepth/isOrphan\n\napp.js:\n- removes _seenPacketIds: new Set() from data\n- removes _seenPacketIds seed from localStorage msgHistory restore in init()\n\napp-ws.js:\n- TEXT_MESSAGE_APP live packet handler: removes _seenPacketIds dedup block;\n  node-dash suppresses duplicates before they reach the browser; browser adds\n  message directly; live entries carry threadRootPktId=pktId, replyDepth=0,\n  isOrphan=false as provisional values until next message_history replay'}
