2026-06-29 09:12:15,994 841080 DEBUG mcpp_git.tool CALL dev_commit args={'message': 'fix: node-dash — MAC-suffix selector, alert dedup timing, IMAP UTF-8 truncation\n\napp-devices.js:\n- _rebuildDeviceConfigs: fallback key is raw MAC (not !hexid) for non-live devices\n- primaryDeviceId: remove endsWith MAC-suffix matching; use direct node_id check\n  then exact MAC check — correct for RAK nRF52840 and any device where firmware\n  node_id does not match MAC suffix\n- rotatorDeviceId: same pattern — no suffix arithmetic\n\ndb.js:\n- Add _alertedPacketIds in-memory Set (cap 2000) for session-level alert dedup\n- isPacketAlerted: check Set first; fall through to DB only if not found\n- markPacketAlerted: add to Set then run best-effort DB UPDATE\n- Fixes race where ws-relay calls markPacketAlerted before persist.js inserts row\n\nimap-receiver.js:\n- Add truncateUtf8Bytes() helper (Buffer encode → byte slice → decode)\n- Replace .slice(0, 228) with truncateUtf8Bytes(text, 228)\n- Fixes over-length payloads for multi-byte UTF-8 characters (emoji, CJK)', 'project': 'node-dash', 'task': 'messages-audit-fixes'}
2026-06-29 09:12:15,994 841080 DEBUG mcpp_git.tool CALL dev_commit args={'message': 'fix: node-dash — MAC-suffix selector, alert dedup timing, IMAP UTF-8 truncation\n\napp-devices.js:\n- _rebuildDeviceConfigs: fallback key is raw MAC (not !hexid) for non-live devices\n- primaryDeviceId: remove endsWith MAC-suffix matching; use direct node_id check\n  then exact MAC check — correct for RAK nRF52840 and any device where firmware\n  node_id does not match MAC suffix\n- rotatorDeviceId: same pattern — no suffix arithmetic\n\ndb.js:\n- Add _alertedPacketIds in-memory Set (cap 2000) for session-level alert dedup\n- isPacketAlerted: check Set first; fall through to DB only if not found\n- markPacketAlerted: add to Set then run best-effort DB UPDATE\n- Fixes race where ws-relay calls markPacketAlerted before persist.js inserts row\n\nimap-receiver.js:\n- Add truncateUtf8Bytes() helper (Buffer encode → byte slice → decode)\n- Replace .slice(0, 228) with truncateUtf8Bytes(text, 228)\n- Fixes over-length payloads for multi-byte UTF-8 characters (emoji, CJK)', 'project': 'node-dash', 'task': 'messages-audit-fixes'}
